<h1> Dice Game </h1>
<br></br>
<p>Welcome.</p>
<p>Here are the rules:</p>

<p>Roll the dice to start the game.</p>
<p>If your first roll is a 7 or 11, you win.</p>
<p>If your first roll is a 2, 3 or 12, you lose.</p>
<p>Anything else becomes your point. Roll your point again before a 7 and you win.</p>

